title: Amitabh Bachchan's granddaughter Navya to debut at Parisian ball
text:
Amitabh Bachchan 's granddaughter Navya Naveli Nanda will make a glamorous debut at le Bal des Débutantes in Paris in November.
Le Bal des Débutantes is the annual debutante ball that brings together 25 girls aged 16 to 22 belonging to prestigious families from around the globe.*Amitabh Bachchan's granddaughter Navya Naveli ... »
